====Usage notes====
''Frei'' can mean “free of charge” only in the context of public services, e.g. ''freie Krankenversorgung'' ("free medical care"), and in some fixed expressions such as {{term|Freibier||free beer|lang=de}} or {{term|freie Kost und Logis||free board and lodge|lang=de}}. Otherwise, ''frei'' is not applicable in this sense.

